'''維吾爾人'''，是[[土耳其|土耳其]]民族中的小族群。

==人口==
在土耳其的維吾爾人人口一直有爭議，但2018年的人口普查表明有10,000多名維吾爾人居住在土耳其<ref name=economist />。但是，由於兩國之間的聯繫已有悠久的歷史，而且兩族都講突厥語，因此這個數字仍然引起很大爭議。[[美國之音|美國之音]]估計有超過45,000名維吾爾人生活在土耳其，其中有10,000人為難民<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.voanews.com/extremism-watch/uighurs-concerned-china-luring-turkey-silence-xinjiang|title=Uighurs Concerned China Is Luring Turkey into Silence on Xinjiang | Voice of America - English|publisher=VOA|access-date=2021-02-24|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126201007/https://www.voanews.com/extremism-watch/uighurs-concerned-china-luring-turkey-silence-xinjiang|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==歷史==
由於土耳其是突厥語國家，因此維吾爾人在很大程度上已經融入了土耳其社會。土耳其一直是逃離[[新疆衝突|新疆衝突]]的維吾爾族人的落腳點<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/2019/05/12/middleeast/turkey-uyghur-community-intl/index.html|title=China's persecuted Uyghurs live 'freely' in Turkey|author=Jomana Karadsheh and Isil Sariyuce|website=CNN|access-date=2021-02-24|archive-date=2019-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190518033842/https://www.cnn.com/2019/05/12/middleeast/turkey-uyghur-community-intl/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，希望移民到歐洲和美國的維吾爾族人經常選擇土耳其作為中途站<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://brill.com/view/book/edcoll/9789004417342/BP000010.xml|title=Experiences of Uyghur Migration to Turkey and the United States: Issues of Religion, Law, Society, Residence, and Citizenship|first=Mettursun|last=Beydulla|date=November 6, 2019|publisher=Brill|access-date=2021-02-24|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204045214/https://brill.com/view/book/edcoll/9789004417342/BP000010.xml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。土耳其一直對新疆的局勢感到關切，儘管它因無實際幫助而受到批評<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://orientxxi.info/magazine/the-uyghur-tragedy-an-embarrassment-for-turkey,3332|title=The Uyghur Tragedy: An Embarrassment for Turkey|first=Bayram|last=Balci|date=October 10, 2019|website=Orient XXI|access-date=2021-02-24|archive-date=2021-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211118205613/https://orientxxi.info/magazine/the-uyghur-tragedy-an-embarrassment-for-turkey,3332|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

自[[敘利亞內戰|敘利亞內戰]]以來，維吾爾人參加了多個聖戰團體，據信其中一些與土耳其政府有聯繫。土耳其的維吾爾族為他們做出了部分貢獻，特別是[[敘利亞突厥斯坦伊斯蘭黨|敘利亞突厥斯坦伊斯蘭黨]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=An Overview of Chinese Fighters and Anti-Chinese Militant Groups in Syria and Iraq |url=https://jamestown.org/program/an-overview-of-chinese-fighters-and-anti-chinese-militant-groups-in-syria-and-iraq/#.VX3kqEZGR9g |author=Jacob Zenn |date=October 10, 2014 |publisher=Jamestown Foundation |access-date=2021-02-24 |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301203238/https://jamestown.org/program/an-overview-of-chinese-fighters-and-anti-chinese-militant-groups-in-syria-and-iraq/#.VX3kqEZGR9g |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]境內也有維吾爾族戰鬥人員。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-mideast-crisis-syria-china-idUSKBN1840UP|title=Syria says up to 5,000 Chinese Uighurs fighting in militant groups|first=Ben|last=Blanchard|date=May 11, 2017|publisher=Reuters|access-date=2021-02-24|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806080232/https://www.reuters.com/article/uk-mideast-crisis-syria-china-idUSKBN1840UP|dead-url=no}}</ref>

